metadata.name: Pelican dreams
metadata.description:
From the Noire series. 
The deep black background is designed to help the viewer not to be distracted by unnecessary details and fully concentrate his attention on the animal, literally look into its soul, to try to find out its character, similar to the portrait of a person.

My Noire series was awarded by numerous awards in many world photography contests, including the 1st place in International Photography Awards (IPA) in Nature category. 


1/1 Edition, Digital Photograph

Title "Pelican dreams"
Collection: Noire
Artist: Yevhen Samuchenko (Q-lieb-in)
